    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm wondering though, when schools say this is \"necessary\" for inclusivity, is that actually a settled thing? like, is there any real pedagogical evidence that teaching this to little kids is better for them, or is it more of just a political thing the school board is doing?",
